2
00:00:28,995 --> 00:00:31,657
打我，打我…
Hit me! Hit me...

3
00:00:36,636 --> 00:00:43,337
快点，打我，再打，打我…
Hit me, hit me again

4
00:00:44,277 --> 00:00:47,735
求求你打我，再打
C'mon, hit me! As hard as you can

5
00:02:05,125 --> 00:02:05,648
你先喝
You drink this first

6
00:02:05,859 --> 00:02:07,121
不
No!

7
00:02:07,494 --> 00:02:08,688
怕什么？
What're you scared of?

8
00:02:08,895 --> 00:02:10,226
不要，我不喝
No, I won't drink

9
00:02:10,530 --> 00:02:12,430
我先喝一口，你再喝吧
c'mon, I'll have a sip first, then your turn

10
00:02:38,791 --> 00:02:40,588
今天晚上可以有点享受了
Let's enjoy ourselves tonight

11
00:02:40,793 --> 00:02:42,420
讨厌，你这个坏人
I hate you, you're a scoundrel

12
00:02:50,670 --> 00:02:51,659
你怎么搞的！
What's wrong with you?

13
00:02:54,407 --> 00:02:56,204
我，我不是有意的
I didn't mean it

14
00:02:57,310 --> 00:02:59,972
打他，重重的打他
Hit him! Hit him hard

15
00:03:14,961 --> 00:03:16,588
志宏，志宏
Zhihong

16
00:03:18,431 --> 00:03:20,592
又臭又脏，讨厌死了
It's dirty and smells

17
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:28,337
好了
It's over

18
00:03:28,541 --> 00:03:30,873
拿着    谢谢
-Here you go -Thanks

19
00:03:31,144 --> 00:03:33,009
走开，走开，别阻我做生意
Get lost, I'm running a business here

20
00:03:33,980 --> 00:03:35,538
走…
Beat it

21
00:03:41,487 --> 00:03:42,613
你一天到晚看报纸
You aren't being paid to read the newspaper

22
00:03:42,822 --> 00:03:44,414
赶快干活去
Get to work

23
00:05:49,882 --> 00:05:51,406
志宏
Zhihong

24
00:06:32,225 --> 00:06:34,250
陈志宏，你想拆房子啊
What, you wanna bring the place down?

25
00:06:34,460 --> 00:06:36,587
你神经病，你不要打烂我的东西啊
Are you crazy? Stop breaking my stuff

26
00:06:37,497 --> 00:06:40,625
什么玩儿，他妈的，神经病
What's the matter with you?

27
00:07:06,626 --> 00:07:08,116
这个我帮你包起来
Ill wrap this up for you

28
00:07:10,630 --> 00:07:14,828
秀…秀娟，我…
Xiujuan, I...

29
00:07:15,034 --> 00:07:17,400
谢谢五块钱，不贵的
Five dollars only, it's cheap

30
00:07:17,970 --> 00:07:19,028
包起来
Wrap it up

31
00:07:19,639 --> 00:07:20,663
等一等呀
Please wait

32
00:07:22,375 --> 00:07:25,344
他挺可怜的，到处受人欺负
Poor thing, he gets bullied everywhere!

33
00:07:52,438 --> 00:07:53,462
随便坐
Have a seat

34
00:07:59,912 --> 00:08:01,345
你们请外卖？
You're hiring a delivery man?

35
00:08:01,881 --> 00:08:02,939
老板在后面
The boss is at the back

36
00:08:13,226 --> 00:08:13,920
老板在那里？
The boss is right there

37
00:08:14,126 --> 00:08:15,150
在那
Over there

38
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:24,434
老板…
Boss

39
00:08:26,072 --> 00:08:27,699
做事要勤快，不能偷懒
You have to be hardworking

40
00:08:27,907 --> 00:08:28,999
不能在街上闲荡
And don't wander around on the streets

41
00:08:29,208 --> 00:08:30,800
早上十点到晚上十一点
10 a.m. to 11p.m.

42
00:08:31,010 --> 00:08:32,307
有一单就要送一单
You'll deliver order by order

43
00:08:32,512 --> 00:08:33,274
一个月四百块
Four hundred dollars a month

44
00:08:33,479 --> 00:08:35,413
店里不包吃不包睡
You don't eat or sleep here

45
00:08:35,615 --> 00:08:36,946
打烂碗碟要赔，你干不干？
And you'll pay for dishes you break, alright?

46
00:08:37,149 --> 00:08:38,081
干，干
Yes, I will take the job

47
00:09:11,384 --> 00:09:12,749
三万    碰
-30,000! -Triple!

48
00:09:39,879 --> 00:09:43,076
喂，你怎么到我这里来呀
Hey, what are you doing here?

49
00:09:54,627 --> 00:09:58,461
哎呀，血，好可怜啊
It's blood, you poor thing

50
00:09:59,198 --> 00:10:00,688
给他们取了蛇胆
They took your gall bladder

51
00:10:01,300 --> 00:10:02,790
就给扔了
And then you got thrown away,

52
00:10:09,909 --> 00:10:13,572
真是的，他们也太残忍啦
it's so cruel

53
00:10:14,146 --> 00:10:15,773
不管你的死活，对不对？
They don't care whether you live or die

54
00:10:16,215 --> 00:10:17,842
不用怕
Don't be scared

55
00:10:19,018 --> 00:10:22,112
好，我给你包扎一下
I'll take care of your wound

56
00:10:25,791 --> 00:10:27,782
我拿点东西给你止血
Let me get something to stop the bleeding

57
00:10:30,329 --> 00:10:33,924
你给人拿了蛇胆，要不把伤口医好
I'll have to attend to the wound...

58
00:10:34,133 --> 00:10:36,260
过不了一个礼拜你就会死了
or else you'll be dead in a week

59
00:10:37,837 --> 00:10:40,169
不要怕呀，我给你缝好
Don't be scared, there'll be stitches

60
00:10:43,843 --> 00:10:45,276
不要怕疼
It won't hurt

61
00:10:48,748 --> 00:10:51,945
好好的休息休息，过几天就会好
Have a good rest, you'll heal in a few days

62
00:10:58,591 --> 00:11:01,082
不要紧，我轻轻的缝，不要怕
Don't worry, I'll be gentle

63
00:11:04,363 --> 00:11:05,625
接好了
It's done

64
00:11:05,931 --> 00:11:08,900
他们这些人，为了迷信蛇胆的功用
They are too cruel, the gall bladder's use...

65
00:11:09,101 --> 00:11:10,659
就把你的胆割了
is exaggerated, they shouldn't have

66
00:11:11,303 --> 00:11:14,466
其实蛇的生命跟人一样宝贵
A snake's life is just as precious as human's

67
00:11:15,574 --> 00:11:17,235
你说是不是？
Do you agree?

68
00:11:34,694 --> 00:11:36,457
你好像听懂我的话对不对？
You seem to understand me

69
00:11:37,229 --> 00:11:38,924
我告诉你，我跟他们不一样
I'm not like them

70
00:11:39,131 --> 00:11:42,157
你放心，乖乖地躺下，盖好
So stay put and have a good rest

71
00:11:42,368 --> 00:11:43,733
好好睡觉呀
Have a good sleep

72
00:12:31,117 --> 00:12:37,352
秀…秀娟，我…我不知道你会来
Xiujuan, I didn't expect to find you here!

73
00:13:12,958 --> 00:13:15,483
原来是你呀，爬得那么快
Oh, it's you! Look at you

74
00:13:16,328 --> 00:13:17,556
伤口好了没有？
Has the wound healed?

75
00:13:28,774 --> 00:13:30,537
呃，快好了吗？
Seem to be doing quite well

76
00:13:39,652 --> 00:13:40,550
只要你听我的话
Just listen to me

77
00:13:40,753 --> 00:13:42,721
再过几天你一定跟以前一样
You'll recover in a couple of days

78
00:13:44,990 --> 00:13:46,548
你爬得那么快
Look at how you're crawling!

79
00:13:47,760 --> 00:13:49,250
我叫你小彪，好不好？
Ill name you Xiaobiao, alright?

80
00:13:49,461 --> 00:13:54,592
好，小彪，乖乖的睡觉吧
Right, Xiaobiao, go to sleep now

81
00:14:03,809 --> 00:14:05,572
你还有什么话想告诉我？
Anything you want to tell me?

82
00:14:27,166 --> 00:14:28,497
我又找到朋友了
I've found another friend

83
00:14:37,142 --> 00:14:38,666
都是给人拿了胆
They all got their gall bladders taken out

84
00:14:42,381 --> 00:14:44,440
你是不是要我帮他们医好？
Do you want me to help them?

85
00:14:45,384 --> 00:14:47,511
好，你的朋友就是我的朋友
No problem, your friends are my friends too

86
00:14:47,853 --> 00:14:49,753
我一定替他们医好，你放心
I'll heal them

87
00:14:51,590 --> 00:14:52,989
不用谢
You're welcome

88
00:15:06,538 --> 00:15:09,701
收工了，你这份工作很好
You're off already? Your job seems to be good

89
00:15:09,909 --> 00:15:10,898
算是长久的了
You've worked there for a while now

90
00:15:12,444 --> 00:15:14,036
自己又没本事
I have no qualifications

91
00:15:14,246 --> 00:15:15,543
做什么全是一样的
All jobs are the same

92
00:15:16,448 --> 00:15:20,646
不过我总算做得下去
But I can keep working at this one

93
00:15:22,655 --> 00:15:23,781
秀娟
Xiujuan

94
00:15:25,090 --> 00:15:25,920
什么事
Yes?

95
00:15:26,792 --> 00:15:32,128
昨天我领了工钱，我想请你看戏
I'd like to take you to a movie

96
00:15:32,798 --> 00:15:36,325
好，午夜场你在翡翠戏院门口等我
How about the midnight show tonight?

97
00:15:41,440 --> 00:15:42,304
晚上见
See you tonight then

98
00:15:54,486 --> 00:15:55,680
有空，再来坐啊
Come again

99
00:15:57,356 --> 00:15:58,550
你们叫的东西来了
Hey, your take-away order is here

100
00:16:00,392 --> 00:16:01,290
对不起
Sorry

101
00:16:01,493 --> 00:16:03,222
死人呀，你什么不长眼睛的！
Damn, couldn't you be a bit more careful?

102
00:16:05,331 --> 00:16:06,355
对不起
Sorry

103
00:16:09,902 --> 00:16:12,063
喂，看什么，有什么好看的
What are you looking at?

104
00:16:12,371 --> 00:16:13,360
没看过？
Haven't you seen a woman before?

105
00:16:19,144 --> 00:16:21,305
看清楚点，你妈妈也是这个样子
Look closer, your mother is similar to me

106
00:16:24,016 --> 00:16:26,246
看呀！你…
Have an eyeful! You...

107
00:16:32,992 --> 00:16:33,981
他妈的！
Damn

108
00:16:35,427 --> 00:16:37,691
看啊！不要钱，赶快看啊
I won't charge, look!

109
00:16:38,297 --> 00:16:40,162
看啊…！
Look!

110
00:16:41,567 --> 00:16:43,967
看啊！
Look!

111
00:16:44,436 --> 00:16:48,395
好了，你们不要欺负他了
That's enough, leave him alone

112
00:17:31,917 --> 00:17:32,815
起来
Get up!

113
00:17:37,489 --> 00:17:38,922
钱呢？藏什么去了？
Where did your money go?

114
00:17:44,797 --> 00:17:45,729
说！
Tell us!

115
00:17:46,598 --> 00:17:47,895
把衣服脱了搜
Strip search

116
00:18:25,337 --> 00:18:26,565
他妈的
Damn!

117
00:18:34,980 --> 00:18:36,072
走
Go

118
00:18:59,171 --> 00:19:01,731
秀娟，你爸爸病重就快不行啦
Xiujuan, your father's dying

119
00:19:03,175 --> 00:19:05,302
你快去呀，不然来不及，快点
You better hurry

120
00:19:07,246 --> 00:19:08,645
这里你不要管，快点去吧
Never mind that, c'mon go

121
00:19:08,847 --> 00:19:10,144
这里我帮你收拾
I'll take care of this

122
00:19:20,726 --> 00:19:21,784
开门
Open up

123
00:19:21,994 --> 00:19:24,963
你可回来了，你得赶快想办法
You're back, think of something

124
00:19:25,697 --> 00:19:26,595
死在这可不行哪
He can't just die here

125
00:19:26,798 --> 00:19:27,958
爸爸
Father

126
00:19:28,167 --> 00:19:29,657
你赶快把他送去医院
You've to hurry and send him to the hospital

127
00:19:30,235 --> 00:19:30,997
你看他病成这样子
Look at him

128
00:19:31,203 --> 00:19:31,862
要是他死在这儿
If he dies here...

129
00:19:32,070 --> 00:19:33,435
我房子租不出去了
I can never rent the room out again

130
00:19:33,639 --> 00:19:34,230
那你可要负责啊！
And I'll hold you responsible then

131
00:19:34,439 --> 00:19:35,133
你静一下好不好！
Be quiet

132
00:19:35,340 --> 00:19:36,967
我爸爸不见得会死吗？
My father won't die

133
00:19:37,176 --> 00:19:38,837
哼，你比我还凶呀
You're quite fierce

134
00:19:39,144 --> 00:19:39,974
你赶紧把他弄出去呀
Just hurry and get him out of here

135
00:19:40,279 --> 00:19:42,179
停在街上我可管不着啊
I don't care even if you leave him on the street

136
00:19:42,548 --> 00:19:45,540
秀娟，你可要想办法呀
You'll have to think of something, Xiujuan

137
00:19:45,751 --> 00:19:46,547
这怎么可以呀
I can't do that

138
00:19:46,752 --> 00:19:50,449
我，爸爸
1...Father

139
00:19:52,691 --> 00:19:53,988
三姑，你赶快打电话
Please call the emergency line...

140
00:19:54,193 --> 00:19:55,319
叫救护车来呀
for the ambulance

141
00:19:55,527 --> 00:19:58,826
救护车呀，我去…
The ambulance, alright

142
00:20:00,933 --> 00:20:02,798
秀娟，你可放心吧
Don't worry, Xiujuan

143
00:20:03,001 --> 00:20:04,434
医院会收留你爸爸的
The hospital will take him

144
00:20:04,736 --> 00:20:06,431
他妈的…
Damn

145
00:20:32,497 --> 00:20:34,795
妈的，给我滚，明天不要来了
You're fired, get out of here

146
00:20:37,502 --> 00:20:39,367
我…
<i>A.</i>

147
00:20:39,571 --> 00:20:42,540
我…什么，你看这个打烂了
What? You've broken this

148
00:20:42,741 --> 00:20:44,265
不叫你赔算好的啦
You're lucky you don't have to pay for it

149
00:20:46,812 --> 00:20:50,179
老板，我，我被阿飞抢了
Boss, I got robbed by some hooligans

150
00:20:50,649 --> 00:20:54,813
我看你才是阿飞，滚…
I think you're the hooligan, get lost

151
00:21:08,200 --> 00:21:09,690
排队…
Line up...

152
00:21:10,636 --> 00:21:12,001
两张
Two tickets

153
00:21:12,271 --> 00:21:13,203
只剩一张啦
There's only one left

154
00:21:13,405 --> 00:21:13,962
我要两张
I want two tickets

155
00:21:14,172 --> 00:21:14,900
只剩一张啦
Only one left

156
00:21:15,107 --> 00:21:15,869
我要两张
Two tickets

157
00:21:16,074 --> 00:21:17,632
没有      走开…
-No -Move over

158
00:21:17,943 --> 00:21:19,069
一张
I want one

159
00:21:22,781 --> 00:21:25,909
对不起，客满了
Sorry, it's all sold

160
00:21:28,587 --> 00:21:36,961
两张…
Two tickets...

161
00:22:50,702 --> 00:22:53,330
秀娟，我不早就劝你做舞女
I've been telling you to be a call girl...

162
00:22:54,873 --> 00:22:56,465
你不肯，要是你听了我的话
if only you'd listen

163
00:22:56,675 --> 00:22:57,266
你爸早就好了
It'll fetch you money to cure your father

164
00:22:57,476 --> 00:22:58,568
怎么会死呢？
And then he won't die, will he?

165
00:23:01,446 --> 00:23:03,778
喂，你欠的房租到底给不给
Hey, you still owe the rent

166
00:23:04,583 --> 00:23:07,677
喂，我跟你说话呀，你怎么不理
Hey, I'm talking to you!

167
00:23:08,453 --> 00:23:10,944
房子是你要租的，我不能让你白住
You'll have to pay the rent...

168
00:23:11,256 --> 00:23:12,052
你到底什么时候给呀！
when will you pay it?

169
00:23:12,257 --> 00:23:13,281
她欠你几个月？
How much does she owe you?

170
00:23:13,492 --> 00:23:14,254
一个月
One month's rent

171
00:23:15,260 --> 00:23:17,387
四十元，真不要脸
Forty dollars

172
00:23:17,629 --> 00:23:19,893
老头死了就想赖租
Just because your father's dead

173
00:23:20,098 --> 00:23:20,587
你再不给
You still have to pay the rent or...

174
00:23:20,799 --> 00:23:21,322
我就要报警
I'll call the police

175
00:23:21,533 --> 00:23:23,899
好了好了，拿去吧
Fine, here are the forty dollars

176
00:23:30,809 --> 00:23:34,745
秀娟，你还是跟我走吧
Xiujuan, you better come with me

177
00:23:40,352 --> 00:23:44,254
我带你去见大班，凭你这个样
I'll take you to my boss, you are pretty

178
00:23:44,456 --> 00:23:46,117
那怕没钱赚
You can start earning money right away

179
00:23:46,558 --> 00:23:48,082
你先搬到我那儿去住
For the time being you can stay with me

180
00:23:49,161 --> 00:23:50,594
看你土里土气也不像样
You look like a country pumpkin though

181
00:23:50,796 --> 00:23:52,889
我好好给你打扮，包你会红的
I'll help you to dress up, you'll be popular

182
00:23:53,765 --> 00:23:54,891
怎么样？
What do you think?

183
00:25:16,648 --> 00:25:18,377
你又要跟我说什么？
You want to tell me something?

184
00:25:35,333 --> 00:25:38,928
小彪，你真是我的好朋友
Xiaobiao, you're my pal

185
00:25:47,612 --> 00:25:49,580
你想安慰我是不是
You want to comfort me, right?

186
00:25:50,815 --> 00:25:54,649
你对我真好，你晓得我喜欢的是谁
You're so nice, do you know whom I fancy?

187
00:25:54,953 --> 00:25:56,477
你真的不晓得
You wouldn't know

188
00:25:57,622 --> 00:26:00,056
是对面卖玩具的秀娟
Xiujuan, who sells toys over at the street

189
00:26:01,660 --> 00:26:05,118
今天晚上我约她看戏
Asked her out for a movie tonight

190
00:26:06,031 --> 00:26:07,396
她没有来
She didn't show up

191
00:26:09,301 --> 00:26:11,667
我一气就把她摊子给打坏
I trashed her stand in a rage

192
00:26:11,970 --> 00:26:13,870
是我不好，她这么关心我
It's my fault, she's very nice to me

193
00:26:14,072 --> 00:26:15,130
我对不起她
I shouldn't have done it

194
00:26:17,709 --> 00:26:19,233
你真懂我的心意
You know exactly what's on my mind

195
00:26:19,911 --> 00:26:22,004
我真喜欢跟你做朋友
I love being friends with you

196
00:26:31,456 --> 00:26:36,484
人家都欺负我，只有你们对我好
They all bully me, only you're kind

197
00:26:38,964 --> 00:26:42,024
现在要吃蛇，最好是吃眼镜蛇
This is the best season to savour cobras

198
00:26:56,915 --> 00:26:57,677
阿忠呀
