有第一次，就有第二次
If there's a first time, there'll be a second

398
01:16:59,848 --> 01:17:01,839
谁有钱谁就能玩她
Whoever has money can have a go

399
01:17:02,384 --> 01:17:08,755
不，不会的…
No, No, No

400
01:17:13,128 --> 01:17:20,762
秀娟，谁有钱，谁就能玩弄你
Xiujuan, whoever has money can touch you

401
01:17:21,570 --> 01:17:25,370
我看你还是死了好
I think you'd be better off dead

402
