Xiujuan, I promise you

405
01:18:24,599 --> 01:18:27,033
我不会饶过他
I'll take revenge for you

406
01:19:33,702 --> 01:19:35,397
搬家？
Moving away?

407
01:20:54,382 --> 01:20:58,944
小彪，小彪，替秀娟报仇
Xiaobiao, kill for Xiujuan

408
01:25:07,469 --> 01:25:08,766
胡宝春
Hu Baochun

409
01:25:09,137 --> 01:25:12,629
你糟蹋了秀娟，要不是我救了她
You ruined Xiujuan, lucky that I've saved her

410
01:25:12,841 --> 01:25:16,208
她酒醒后会比蛇咬更痛苦
from her despair

411
01:25:16,978 --> 01:25:19,003
你比这些蛇还要毒
You're more wicked than venom

412
01:26:21,376 --> 01:26:22,400
他好像不在
I don't think he's in

413
01:26:22,744 --> 01:26:23,711
再看看
Look again

414
01:26:24,145 --> 01:26:25,476
不用找了，他不在里面
He's not inside

415
01:26:26,247 --> 01:26:27,976
昨天他拿了东西走啦
He took a lot of stuff with him

416
01:26:29,384 --> 01:26:30,408
你是干什么的？
Who are you?

417
01:26:30,752 --> 01:26:32,686
我在蛇铺隔壁开理发店
I'm the hairdresser next door

418
01:27:16,598 --> 01:27:17,826
他可能真的搬走了
He might have really moved

419
01:27:18,199 --> 01:27:19,860
是啊，昨天晚上我真的
Yes, I saw him last night

420
01:27:20,068 --> 01:27:21,968
看见他搬了一大堆东西走了
He took a lot of stuff with him

421
01:27:22,170 --> 01:27:24,070
有什么证据证明他已经搬走了
What evidence have you got that he's moved?

422
01:27:25,306 --> 01:27:26,466
你们跟我来吧
Please come with me

423
01:28:22,764 --> 01:28:23,731
走吧      好
-Let's go -OK

424
01:29:30,264 --> 01:29:31,288
小彪
Xiaobiao

425
