原谅我，我实在不愿意这样做
Please forgive me, I have no choice

426
01:29:36,904 --> 01:29:38,997
我只是不愿意警察抓到你们
I just don't want the police to capture you

427
01:29:39,640 --> 01:29:40,902
虐待你们
And they'll torture you

428
01:29:42,844 --> 01:29:46,245
